Novatek May Buy 51% of Northgas From Gazprom, Vedomosti Reports

-- B y   S c o t t   R o s e
-- 
2011-04-28T04:21:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/novatek-may-buy-51-of-northgas-from-gazprom-vedomosti-reports.html
OAO Novatek wants to purchase 51
percent of gas producer Northgas from OAO Gazprom,  Vedomosti
reported .  Gazprom Chief Executive Officer  Alexei Miller  has
tentatively approved a price for the sale, which may interrupt
OAO Inter RAO UES’s purchase of 49 percent in Northgas from
businessman Farkhad Akhmedov, the Moscow-based newspaper
reported today, citing people close to Gazprom and Northgas.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Scott Rose in Moscow at 
 rrose10@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
 bpenz@bloomberg.net . 